{"tid":2431764,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"立陶宛擬在台灣設處 脫離中國與中東歐合作機制","createTime":"2021-03-04T01:16:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T14:45:41.000Z","uid":138409,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e1a10147f3e6e653ccfeb939b3cfbd870d95efeb","tid":2431764,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T01:16:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202103030128.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F202103030128.aspx&d=UjOWczzRfTNgHoC3e3JiX7XdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=89cd9025\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202103030128.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n立陶宛國家廣播電視台（LRT）2日報導，立陶宛國會外交委員會2月通過決議，支持立陶宛脫離北京主導的「17+1」、也就是中國與中東歐17國的合作機制。<br />\n<br />\n前資深外交官、現任國會外交委員會主席帕維里奧尼斯（Žygimantas Pavilionis）表示，中國企圖透過這個機制接管中東歐各國的基礎建設，立陶宛不應該冒險。<br />\n<br />\n帕維里奧尼斯還說，立陶宛應該轉與區域內的其它民主國家合作，「立陶宛正計劃與台灣擴展關係和成立經濟代表處」。<br />\n<br />\n立陶宛外長藍斯柏吉斯（Gabrielius Landsbergis）在國會通過決議後也指出，北京與中東歐17國的合作機制「幾乎沒給立陶宛帶來好處」，而且由於各國對中國立場不同，會導致歐洲被分化。<br />\n<br />\n不過他強調，立陶宛不是現在就離開，而是應該考慮推動對中關係比較有效的方法。<br />\n<br />\n中國為拉攏中東歐國家創立的「17+1」合作機制，近年由於投資承諾沒有兌現和歐洲有被分化的危險備受批評。2月舉行的年度峰會，立陶宛、羅馬尼亞等6國僅派部長參加，創下歷年參與層級最低的紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n相較之下，由於有脫離蘇聯獨立的歷史經驗，對受到大國威脅能感同身受，台灣在立陶宛政界被視為是民主的典範。<br />\n<br />\n在國會友台小組成員艾德梅納斯（Mantas Adomėnas）的領銜下，包含50位國會議員在內的逾200位政壇和知識界菁英，去年4月聯名致函總統瑙塞達（Gitanas Nausėda），支持台灣加入國際組織和在台成立代表處。<br />\n<br />\n去年10月大選後上台的祖國聯盟（Homeland Union）等3個政黨，在聯合執政協定中並承諾將推動「以價值觀為依據的外交政策」，「捍衛世界各地為自由而奮鬥的人，從白俄羅斯到台灣」。（編輯：黃自強）1100303<br />\n<br />\n立陶宛位於東歐，與愛沙尼亞、拉脫維亞合稱波羅的海三小國。（<a href=\"http://圖取自Google地圖網頁google.com/maps\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%9C%96%E5%8F%96%E8%87%AAGoogle%E5%9C%B0%E5%9C%96%E7%B6%B2%E9%A0%81google.com%2Fmaps&d=UjOWczzRfTNgHoC3e3JiX7XdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=32ebfb71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">圖取自Google地圖網頁google.com/maps</a>）"},{"pid":"8f68cefdf335c37085618866357af29cd1255540","tid":2431764,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T01:21:25.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"77a82b0eda5f0f2e97be972594b3a44ebaac6249","tid":2431764,"uid":44028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T01:21:41.000Z","msg":"十卜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e14d06cf8380cfdfdbfe00f58e2b8ca31579803b","tid":2431764,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T01:24:12.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"41eeb173634c3f26e2c6eee7ed814804bb469789","tid":2431764,"uid":51820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T01:25:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ab9acbdd23cbdfe00f8a4578a9938df55af19308","tid":2431764,"uid":64337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T01:25:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae28d6e7312ab67844fe5a9d74159773ad44021f","tid":2431764,"uid":331739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T01:26:15.000Z","msg":"建交未？"},{"pid":"3c149a2e17793112e985939916f0f96e80649cbd","tid":2431764,"uid":337119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T05:48:17.000Z","msg":"堅定支持加入Free World聯盟"},{"pid":"974e67c145255ba512837176883cdeaa8c717b7a","tid":2431764,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T05:51:28.000Z","msg":"反檯啦屌"},{"pid":"2a3fadd0d80dfb8d29424609ca1a111fd8a2eb8d","tid":2431764,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T14:41:26.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58eea97ae35b82a21e69fa6c230a9d4a585c154e","tid":2431764,"uid":60366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T14:45:02.000Z","msg":"立陶宛人不嬲好撚憎共產黨"},{"pid":"32f2826bbeb4148c3571559ba311c6aead6ed265","tid":2431764,"uid":218158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T14:45:41.000Z","msg":"之前歐盟開完會傾白羅啲嘢，立陶宛立即就禁止白羅總統入國"}]}